comments.body: I heard we have to pay advance payment before 5th June without knowing about being selected or not ,is it true how does it work anybody knows?

> mods please don't delete koi idea toh lag jaega yaar  

1. There is no data to use to make predictions. This is the first time we have JEE for admissions. 
2. The people making predictions are just like you - aspirants looking for colleges. 

So you're basically receiving counseling advice from those who have no idea about the system, haven't gone through this process before, and don't have any facts to make predictions. 

Don't be a clown and get out of this blind leading the blind behavior.
